352
00:18:50,755 --> 00:18:52,381
It smells really good.

353
00:18:52,465 --> 00:18:54,342
-It smells good.
-Yeah.

354
00:18:55,468 --> 00:18:57,136
-I think that's good.
-Is it?

355
00:19:02,725 --> 00:19:04,268
Watch out.

356
00:19:04,352 --> 00:19:05,728
Looks amazing.

357
00:19:06,604 --> 00:19:09,649
-Where are you going?
-I was gonna watch a movie.

358
00:19:09,732 --> 00:19:11,150
-Got it.
-You're not eating?

359
00:19:11,233 --> 00:19:12,610
It's okay.

360
00:19:17,198 --> 00:19:18,866
-Bon appétit.
-Bon appétit.

361
00:19:18,949 --> 00:19:21,160
-Thanks, Uchi.
-Thank you.

362
00:19:21,994 --> 00:19:23,412
-Bon appétit.
-Bon appétit.

