00:20:09,750 --> 00:20:11,460
There's a guy from Hawaii.

378
00:20:12,503 --> 00:20:13,838
His name is Arman.

379
00:20:15,131 --> 00:20:19,093
We get along, but he's always home.

380
00:20:20,010 --> 00:20:21,595
I wish...

