00:20:28,018 --> 00:20:29,019
Really?

385
00:20:29,103 --> 00:20:31,397
Great personality though.

386
00:20:31,480 --> 00:20:34,400
I wouldn't recommend a guy like him.

387
00:20:35,484 --> 00:20:38,404
It should be someone who works.

388
00:20:38,487 --> 00:20:41,449
And the new guy who arrived
at the same time as me...

389
00:20:42,366 --> 00:20:45,411
