390
00:20:45,494 --> 00:20:50,583
Manly, but a little boyish,
straightforward...

391
00:20:51,500 --> 00:20:52,877
but he's 18.

392
00:20:52,960 --> 00:20:54,086
So young!

393
00:20:55,004 --> 00:20:56,005
Eighteen, huh?

394
00:20:57,006 --> 00:21:01,802
If he was 27 or something,
