395
00:21:02,678 --> 00:21:04,305
Ready.

396
00:21:08,642 --> 00:21:09,643
Cute.

397
00:21:16,859 --> 00:21:17,860
Nice.

398
00:21:34,835 --> 00:21:36,629
-I'm back.
-Welcome home.

