456
00:25:33,615 --> 00:25:35,868
No, we were wrong.

457
00:25:35,951 --> 00:25:38,036
It's not enough to apologize.

458
00:25:39,288 --> 00:25:40,998
That's all we can do.

459
00:25:42,374 --> 00:25:44,168
That's all I can do.

460
00:25:44,251 --> 00:25:45,627
I'll apologize.

461
00:25:46,628 --> 00:25:48,464
But he's so mad.

462
00:25:53,093 --> 00:25:55,804
This is so entertaining.

463
00:25:55,888 --> 00:25:58,807
I didn't know these things happened.

464
00:25:58,891 --> 00:25:59,892
