465
00:25:59,975 --> 00:26:02,352
-In the year 2016.
-You've got to be kidding.

466
00:26:02,436 --> 00:26:05,689
This is new for <i>Terrace House.</i>

467
00:26:05,773 --> 00:26:07,649
This incident has been recorded.

468
00:26:07,733 --> 00:26:10,068
The meat crime topped everything.

469
00:26:11,445 --> 00:26:13,947
The meat crime?

470
00:26:14,031 --> 00:26:16,992
