471
00:26:17,075 --> 00:26:18,452
I thought, "No way."

472
00:26:18,535 --> 00:26:23,499
When Uchi seemed unhappy,
and the camera cut to the empty meat box,

473
00:26:23,582 --> 00:26:25,167
