474
00:26:25,250 --> 00:26:30,130
-I think we all felt that.
-We all thought, "No way."

475
00:26:30,214 --> 00:26:32,132
"That can't be it."

476
00:26:32,216 --> 00:26:35,010
I mean, no one would write a script as,

477
00:26:35,093 --> 00:26:37,429
-"The Meat Crime."
-No way.

478
00:26:37,513 --> 00:26:39,848
-It's so insignificant.
-It would've been vetoed.

479
00:26:39,932 --> 00:26:43,519
Yeah, like who cares.
The meat crime would never happen.

480
00:26:43,602 --> 00:26:45,145
I wonder what he'll think
after he watches this episode?

481
00:26:45,229 --> 00:26:47,689
"Minori said she didn't like it."

482
00:26:48,941 --> 00:26:50,108
-She said it was fatty.
-That's right.

483
00:26:50,192 --> 00:26:53,695
