484
00:26:53,779 --> 00:26:55,364
And the line from the 18-year-old.

485
00:26:55,447 --> 00:26:58,325
"If you don't want us to eat it,
you should leave a note."

486
00:26:59,827 --> 00:27:02,204
Hikaru is right, though.

487
00:27:02,287 --> 00:27:03,288
He's right.

